{"lemma":"ثَغَراتٌ","slug":"ثَغَراتٌ","root":"ث.غ.ر","root_slug":"ث-غ-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ث-غ-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n4459","n4462"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AB%D9%8E%D8%BA%D9%8E%D8%B1%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"gap, loophole, pit, wedge"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From the root ث غ ر (ṯ ḡ r). Doublet of تُرْعَة (turʕa) from Aramaic."},"ipa":["/θuɣ.ra/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n4459","headword_ar":"ثَغَرَهُ","root":"vgr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (T, A, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vagorN","text_ar":"ثَغْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He broke it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, A;) namely, a part of a wall; (A;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he demolished it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"this is [said to be] the primary signification:"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he demolished it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pulled it down;"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely, a wall: (T:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he broke it"},{"kind":"text","text":"(namely, anything, [as a wall and a vessel, &c.,] A)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so as to make a gap in it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a hollow in its edge."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, K.) ―         -b2-  Also, (IAar, S, Msb, K,) aor. as above, (Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He broke his"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vagor","text_ar":"ثَغْر"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"front teeth"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (S, Msb, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his teeth."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, and TA as from the K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vugira","text_ar":"ثُغِرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the pass. form, inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vuguwrN","text_ar":"ثُغُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a boy)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"had his"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vagor","text_ar":"ثَغْر"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"front teeth] broken."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vagarotu sin~ahu","text_ar":"ثَغَرْتُ سِنَّهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I pulled out his tooth."},{"kind":"text","text":"(El-Hujeymee, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vugira","text_ar":"ثُغِرَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"had a tooth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"teeth, pulled out."},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, TA.) ―         -b4-  Also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vugira","text_ar":"ثُغِرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (AZ, S, Mgh, Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vagorN","text_ar":"ثَغْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (AZ, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a boy)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shed his central milk-teeth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ, S, Mgh, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vagor","text_ar":"ثَغْر"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"front teeth"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (AZ, Msb:) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^avogara","text_ar":"اَثْغَرَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"has this latter meaning, (A, K,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ait~agara","text_ar":"اِتَّغَرَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (As, TA;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vagira","text_ar":"ثَغِرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ait~agara","text_ar":"اِتَّغَرَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Sh, TA,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ait~agara","text_ar":"اِتَّغَرَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he shed his teeth:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sh, Msb, K:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vugira","text_ar":"ثُغِرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is said to have this last signification in the Kifáyet el-Mutahaffidh; and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Av~gr","text_ar":"اثّغر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"At~gr","text_ar":"اتّغر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"are there said to have the contr. signification, explained below [see 8]. (Msb.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vugira","text_ar":"ثُغِرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He had his mouth bruised;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^uvogira","text_ar":"اُثْغِرَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vagara Alv~ulomapa","text_ar":"ثَغَرَ الثُّلْمَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He stopped up,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"obstructed, the gap,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"breach:"},{"kind":"text","text":"thus the verb bears two contr. significations. (K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vagaronaAhumo","text_ar":"ثَغَرْنَاهُمْ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We stopped up,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"obstructed, against them the gaps,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"passes of the mountain;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"we stopped up,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"obstructed, against them the place of exit, so that they knew not what way to take."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.)"}],"source_refs":["T","A","K","IAar","S","Msb","AZ","Mgh","Sh","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n4462","headword_ar":"ثُغْرَةٌ","root":"vgr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"; pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vugarN","text_ar":"ثُغَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vagorN","text_ar":"ثَغْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places. ―         -b2-  Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pit of the uppermost part of the breast,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"chest, between the two collar-bones;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K;) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pit in the middle of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHor","text_ar":"نَحْر"},{"kind":"text","text":": pl. as above: (Msb:) in a camel, the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pit which is the stabbingplace:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and in a horse, [the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"part] above the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juw^ojuw^","text_ar":"جُوْجُو"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) which is the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"prominent portion of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHor","text_ar":"نَحْر"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"between the upper parts of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fahodataAn","text_ar":"فَهْدَتَان"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"two portions of flesh on the right and left of the breast"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A tract,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quarter, of the earth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of land;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vagorN","text_ar":"ثَغْرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA bitiloka Alv~ugorapi mivoluhu","text_ar":"مَا بِتِلْكَ الثُّغْرَةِ مِثْلُهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There is not, in that tract,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quarter, of the earth, his,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"its, like."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A plain, level,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"even, road;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vagorN","text_ar":"ثَغْرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any road that people tread,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pass along, with ease;"},{"kind":"text","text":"because they furrow its surface: (T, TA:) pl. as above. (A.) [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vugaru Almasojidi","text_ar":"ثُغَرُ المَسْجِدِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The ways leading to the mosque:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vugorapu Almasojidi","text_ar":"ثُغْرَةُ المَسْجِدِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the upper part of the mosque"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"next to the kibleh"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwayaxotariqu","text_ar":"هُوَيَخْتَرِقُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vugara Almajodi","text_ar":"ثُغَرَ المَجْدِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He travels] the ways of glory."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.)"}],"source_refs":["Msb","K","TA","T"]}]}}